==English==
[[Image:Chisel wood 24mm.jpg|thumb|a wood chisel]]

===Noun===
'''chisel'''

# A [[tool]] consisting of a slim oblong block of metal which is flattened to a [[sharp]] [[edge]] at one end and attached to a [[handle]] at the other end. It is used mainly to [[remove]] parts of [[stone]] or [[wood]] by placing the sharp edge against the material and [[pound]]ing the handle with a [[hammer]].

